<td>1996+</td>
<td>CSS utilizes a weak, <a href="/wiki/40-bit_encryption" title="40-bit encryption">40-bit</a> <a href="/wiki/Stream_cipher" title="Stream cipher">stream cipher</a> to actively encrypt DVD-Video.</td>
